high_descs: Move across the room to the sink.
Pick up the apple out of the sink.
Move to the microwave across the counter.
Put the apple in the microwave to warm it up.  Take it out of the microwave.
Move to the refrigerator across the room.
Put the apple in the fridge. Close the door.

high_descs: Turn left, at end of table turn right.  Turn left at sink, proceed to sink.
Pick up apple from sink, located directly behind the glass.
Open microwave, put apple in microwave, shut door.  Cook for four seconds, open microwave door, remove apple, shut door.
Move to the right to the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator door, place apple on second shelf down, to the left and forward of the egg.  Close refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Cook apple and put it in the refrigerator.
